iddle","imagePosition":"left","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Good-Housekeeping-2022-new.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Good Housekeeping Institute","text":"<p>\"I wish we had found this sooner; it is absolutely perfect and impressive the cover is made from 100% upcycled marine plastic!\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"5590401f-eb77-4089-8722-fbc67e7a2a7b":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--5590401f-eb77-4089-8722-fbc67e7a2a7b img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#ffffff","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"right","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Best_eco_mattress_2022_82d2f114-5baa-4d47-80db-e131c625a4a8.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Best Eco Friendly Mattress","text":"<p>\"REM-Fit have created a fantastic Eco mattress that is made with upcycled ocean plastic and foams and comes at a fair price.\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/bestmattressuk.com\/best-mattress-uk-awards\/#htoc-b","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"5b837213-a830-429f-8f81-5ab42514e192":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--5b837213-a830-429f-8f81-5ab42514e192 img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#f9f9f9","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"left","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/RealHomes_loves_logo_Transparentv2-min_300_1.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Real Homes","text":"<p>\"Supportive, comfortable and competitively priced, we highly rate the REM-Fit 400 hybrid mattress which has two (more) very happy customers\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/www.realhomes.com\/reviews\/rem-fit-400-hybrid-mattress-review","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"7d6a4f52-4d29-4656-b8ce-49d222938cd7":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--7d6a4f52-4d29-4656-b8ce-49d222938cd7 img{\nwidth:40% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"right","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GHA_logo_d70b6f9f-09e1-4d1f-8c8e-2e9fbbba3248.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Good Homes","text":"<p>\"The REM-Fit 600 mattress cradles the weight of the body, providing a soft and sumptuous feel, whilst still delivering great support without the without that weird sinking feeling you can get with some memory foam mattresses.\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/www.goodhomesmagazine.com\/shopping\/review-rem-fit-600-lux-hybrid-mattress\/","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"b6063fdf-ec12-49c7-ae56-6738002cdb56":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--b6063fdf-ec12-49c7-ae56-6738002cdb56 img{\nwidth:25% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#f9f9f9","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"left","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/golden_mattress-min.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"The Mattress Guide","text":"<p>\"REM-Fit has equipped this mattress with all the tools to combat back pain, especially if you are needing a slightly firmer feeling mattress.\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/www.themattressguide.co.uk\/best-mattress-for-back-pain\/","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"d08533ca-be0f-4e54-8625-c21221ea90ba":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--d08533ca-be0f-4e54-8625-c21221ea90ba img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"right","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2021_back_pain_e1384c6f-06bc-4adf-894a-2b2a084b9ba7.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Sleep Goodness","text":"<p>\"The REM-Fit 500 Ortho is an affordable option and I recommend to everyone who suffers from back pain. It’s a hybrid mattress that comes with a firmer feel and it’s built with high-quality materials. It features a 4-layer design and it’s built here in the UK.\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/sleepgoodness.co.uk\/sleep-goodness-awards\/#best-mattress-for-back-pain","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"2cf54e9a-8b84-4ccd-b050-0f84971dcd92":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--2cf54e9a-8b84-4ccd-b050-0f84971dcd92 img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#f9f9f9","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"left","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2021_best_cooling.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Best Cooling Mattress","text":"<p>\"The springs improve airflow and the upper Open Cell foam layer does an excellent job keeping the sleeping surface cool.\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/sleepgoodness.co.uk\/sleep-goodness-awards\/#best-cooling-mattress","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"image_text_fGDcBV":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--image_text_fGDcBV img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment":"middle","imagePosition":"right","imageWidth":"6","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/toms-guide.png","overlayOpacity":0,"overlayColor":"#000000","heading":"Tom's Guide, 2024","text":"<p>\"This mid-range, firm mattress combines tall, motion-absorbing springs with lightly cushioning memory foam and brilliant edge-to-edge support, and will provide outstanding comfort for most back or stomach sleepers, as well as those struggling with back pain\"<\/p>","buttonText":"View Award","url":"https:\/\/www.tomsguide.com\/reviews\/rem-fit-500-ortho-hybrid-mattress","wideButton":false,"buttonType":"primary","buttonStyle":"default"}},"image_text_3LeLpL":{"type":"imageText","settings":{"displayFor":"display--both","layout":"default","nomargin":false,"scopedCSS":"#s--image_text_3LeLpL img{\nwidth:30% !important;\nmargin-left:auto !important;\nmargin-right:auto !Important;\n}","customID":"","height":0,"padding":50,"lineMargin":20,"backgroundColor":"#f9f9f9","contentColor":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","horizontalAlignment":"center","verticalAlignment